    "captions": [
      {
        "text": "A firestorm killed thousands, yet history completely forgot it.",
        "position": {
          "start": 0.16,
          "end": 2.4
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "October 1871. Wisconsin\u2019s Peshtigo region faces a brutal drought.",
        "position": {
          "start": 4.16,
          "end": 8.32
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Clearing fires merge into a monstrous, unstoppable wall of flame.",
        "position": {
          "start": 8.56,
          "end": 11.6
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Witnesses describe a spinning fire tornado lifting houses into the sky.",
        "position": {
          "start": 11.6,
          "end": 15.84
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Over twelve hundred people perish, many drowning in the river.",
        "position": {
          "start": 15.84,
          "end": 21.12
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "But Chicago\u2019s great fire steals every newspaper headline that week.",
        "position": {
          "start": 21.52,
          "end": 25.52
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Survivors rebuild quietly, their trauma buried beneath national distraction.",
        "position": {
          "start": 28.24,
          "end": 31.12
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Today, a quiet museum honors the forgotten dead of Peshtigo.",
        "position": {
          "start": 31.44,
          "end": 34.24
        },
        "style": {
          "font": "System Bold",
          "size": 48,
          "color": "#FFFFFF",
          "stroke": "#000000"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Some tragedies vanish not from lack of impact, but timing.",
